7ï¸âƒ£ Black Box Testing Techniques (Focus Area)
Tester does not see code, only inputs & outputs.

8ï¸âƒ£ Equivalence Partitioning (EP)
What is EP?
Divide input data into valid and invalid partitions and test one value from each.

ğŸ“Œ Example: Age field (18â€“60)
Partition	Example
Valid	25
Invalid	10, 70

ğŸ§  Saves effort by avoiding unnecessary tests.

